TITLE: Configuring Tailwind CSS for React Native
DESCRIPTION: Tailwind CSS configuration for React Native projects with NativeWind preset, specifying content paths and theme extensions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nativewind/nativewind/blob/main/apps/website/docs/getting-started/installation.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
module.exports = {
  // NOTE: Update this to include the paths to all of your component files.
  content: ["./App.{js,jsx,ts,tsx}"],
  presets: [require("nativewind/preset")],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}
```

