TITLE: Implementing Platform-Specific Theming in Tailwind
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the platformSelect and platformColor functions from NativeWind to implement platform-specific theming in a Tailwind configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nativewind/nativewind/blob/main/apps/website/docs/guides/themes.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const { platformSelect, platformColor } = require("nativewind/theme");

module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        error: platformSelect({
          ios: "red",
          android: "blue",
          default: "green",
        }),
        platformRed: platformSelect({
          android: platformColor("systemRed"),
          web: "red",
        }),
      },
    },
  },
};
```

