TITLE: Configuring Blocked Module Transforms in Babel for NativeWind
DESCRIPTION: Advanced Babel configuration that specifies which modules should not be transformed by NativeWind. This example blocks transformation for the 'react-select' module.
SOURCE: https://github.com/nativewind/nativewind/blob/main/apps/website/versioned_docs/version-v2/guides/babel.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// babel.config.js
module.exports = {
  plugins: [
    [
     "nativewind/babel"
     { blockModuleTransform: ["react-select"] }
    ]
  ],
};
```

